metadata.name: Sheriff of the West
metadata.description:
Sheriff of the West is a photo of an old rusted classic sheriff car out front of the general store in Hackberry Az. 

 The clouds were coming in and light was fading away. I had a random pause and drifted off in a slight daydream thinking of old wild west police chases and robberies flying down the dirt roads of Route 66.

Thinking I would not want to be in a chase with this Vehicle of the Law!
